China holds Uighur who 'planned bomb attack': report | News , World | THE DAILY STAR
Armed police officers stand guard near the Erdaoqiao Bazaar in Urumqi, western China's Xinjiang province Saturday, June 29, 2013. (AP Photo/Kyodo News)
